{"tid":1418384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[割]和理勇武必須割","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T18:57:57.000Z","uid":190700,"like":31,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b2092db59287a9f4c61b393547d7207d5697e205","tid":1418384,"uid":190700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢話少講，係想檢討我呢幾日見到既事<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 勇武變速龍</span></ins></span><br />\n請照鏡。<br />\n留意自己嘴臉，同速龍一撚樣，<br />\n麻煩對路人客氣小小，唔好係人都屌，係人都圍。<br />\n<strong>照鏡見到自己，遮好哂啦嗎？</strong>驚乜撚比街坊影，怕咪落雨擔傘。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2.唔撚控火魔法師</strong></span></span></ins><br />\n用技前請留意四周。<br />\n屌你無狗燒垃圾做乜撚？七月燒香？<br />\n有樹就咪撚燒，你唔會控制到，<br />\n到時有消防來滅火你燒來多鳩餘，撚狗定撚消防？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">3.街坊場勇武請咪撚阻住哂。</span></ins></span><br />\n觀塘到我主場做街坊果陣，第一批勇武比人清場<br />\n街坊落場屌走速龍，防暴鳩縮。<br />\n點撚知第二批勇武來到，防暴又出返來。<br />\n近百街坊無gear 係<ins>升級和理非</ins>用肉身頂防暴，<br />\n<em>街坊最前頂狗，勇武掟磚入狗屋掟到唔撚想走</em><br />\n好心玩兩下好走，咪撚要<ins>升級和理非</ins>食煙。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">4.天真和理非</span></strong></ins></span><br />\n<em>咪撚再放施暴者，和理唔該借借</em><br />\n打人既，先制服，再一律用索帶索撚住佢，<br />\n學狗咁反扣上鐵欄，記者又可以影下相，一舉兩得。<br />\n千萬咪再對手上有武器既白衫輕視，要講請有甲既手足講。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">5.請割和理同勇武</span></strong></ins></span><br />\n一天只做一件事，<br />\n今日三罷無成果，因為太多支線，明明香港歷史咁大件事，點解無媒體主力寫？<br />\n今日頭條係和平罷工，政府唔撚回應，聽日再勇武。<br />\n觀感唔會好啲咩？<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n手足繼續升級，全方面都要升級，武力、EQ、IQ&hellip;&hellip;<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\n最後最後<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n守護香港，保衛家園。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39efb2f94f35dc4a1f0370618b8ca0a936c6e7c","tid":1418384,"uid":76216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:35:10.000Z","msg":"建議］ p牌正負評顯示<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dwROzT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dwROzT</a>"},{"pid":"0eb8a9bf830d514b91db1781ef1b3fb385574bfc","tid":1418384,"uid":189068,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:35:17.000Z","msg":"咪撚再玩標題黨啦<br />\n咩時勢"},{"pid":"54a95593d6e83ddcf475f721b0430367ae73d960","tid":1418384,"uid":190700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:35:27.000Z","msg":"打完唔好哂，自推十下"},{"pid":"b5d2d2b02f4fc1ca81d122ccbf1e0343bd4cc02e","tid":1418384,"uid":32502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:35:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母可唔可以唔好再標題黨？"},{"pid":"250053f9a403c8cd6a751ad333f2ba224e53611b","tid":1418384,"uid":190700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:36:01.000Z","msg":"九下"},{"pid":"e5a63075f582da30afcdde0d142c1bbf6c38bd7f","tid":1418384,"uid":96439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:36:08.000Z","msg":"割你老母臭閪呀"},{"pid":"79822e5cfe89c3e0d1c7ea811c9abf16a5ed8c32","tid":1418384,"uid":190700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:36:44.000Z","msg":"真係要割，第五點講到明"},{"pid":"0ac5a4a6b03d0aec9c39e57da0ea8db31706d093","tid":1418384,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:37:30.000Z","msg":"下次邊個再勸交就當敵人打撚埋"},{"pid":"f566086473b09226add0987c3fcdf81825010e0e","tid":1418384,"uid":190700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:37:54.000Z","msg":"唔再分割和理同勇武<br />\n只會各自流失，<br />\n要合作，唔可以同場"},{"pid":"646403d1546b6f5822e2bfd64d49a0b806cf5dc0","tid":1418384,"uid":278168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T